data.description: Spacious home on country setting! Open plan between kitchen/dining/den areas. Fireplace in DR +wood heater in den.Fresh paint in main areas. Island in kitchen w plenty of counter space & storage.  Owner suite is oversized w lots of windows and natural light +area for sitting space&walk in closet. Hall bath recently updated:painted shiplap &soaking tub.  Oversized laundry& pantry areas.Lots of covered attached parking, det garage w extra carport. Garage has concrete floor&greenhouse area.  Detached metal bldg w water access&power(lift remains). RV power hookup.Basement access on front porch. Back yard has drain for rainwater. New concrete on part of front drive. Outdoor fireplaces don't stay.
